{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/use-the-parseint-function-with-a-radix","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Koristite parseInt Funkciju sa Osnovom Brojnog Sistema","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Funkcija <code>parseInt()</code> parsira string i vraca ceo broj. Prima drugi argument za osnovu brojnog sistema (radix), koji opisuje osnovu broja u stringu. Osnova moze biti ceo broj izmedju 2 i 36.</p>\n<p>Poziv funkcije izgleda ovako:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">parseInt(string, radix);\n</code></pre>\n<p>A evo primera:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">const a = parseInt(\"11\", 2);\n</code></pre>\n<p>Argument osnove pokazuje da je <code>11</code> u binarnom sistemu, odnosno bazi 2. Ovaj primer konvertuje string <code>11</code> u ceo broj <code>3</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d7b7e367417b2b2512b22","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Koristite <code>parseInt()</code> u funkciji <code>convertToInteger</code> da konvertujete binarni broj u ceo broj i vratite rezultat.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301182,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/use-the-parseint-function-with-a-radix"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function convertToInteger(str) {\n\n}\n\nconvertToInteger(\"10011\");","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>convertToInteger</code> treba da koristi funkciju <code>parseInt()</code></p>","testString":"assert(/parseInt/g.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)));"},{"text":"<p><code>convertToInteger(\"10011\")</code> treba da vrati broj</p>","testString":"assert(typeof convertToInteger('10011') === 'number');"},{"text":"<p><code>convertToInteger(\"10011\")</code> treba da vrati 19</p>","testString":"assert(convertToInteger('10011') === 19);"},{"text":"<p><code>convertToInteger(\"111001\")</code> treba da vrati 57</p>","testString":"assert(convertToInteger('111001') === 57);"},{"text":"<p><code>convertToInteger(\"JamesBond\")</code> treba da vrati <code>NaN</code></p>","testString":"assert.isNaN(convertToInteger('JamesBond'));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-javascript","dashedName":"use-the-parseint-function-with-a-radix","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-javascript","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/use-the-conditional-ternary-operator","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/use-the-parseint-function","id":"587d7b7e367417b2b2512b22","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum) {\n  if (endNum - startNum === 0) {\n    return [startNum];\n  } else {\n    const numbers = rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum - 1);\n    numbers.push(endNum);\n    return numbers;\n  }\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/use-the-parseint-function-with-a-radix"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}